Sentencas: We tested, by means of simulations, the idea of a patterned contact between composite electrode and electrolyte of a SOFC.
Titulo: Simulation study about the geometry of electrode-electrolyte contact in a SOFC

Sentencas: Simulation results show that the patterned studied geometry can improve the performance of the assembly in intermediate conditions, i.e. when there are neither ohmic nor kinetic limitations.
Titulo: Simulation study about the geometry of electrode-electrolyte contact in a SOFC

Sentencas: The gain reached up to 45 % in terms of current density drawn, with respect to a standard flat contact.
Titulo: Simulation study about the geometry of electrode-electrolyte contact in a SOFC
